title: Diana King-Shy Guy(1995)(DVD Rip)-Wushan.AVI
description:
Shy Guy 

                               Single by Diana King

               from the album Tougher Than Love and Bad Boys soundtrack


    "Shy Guy" is a song by Diana King from the Bad Boys soundtrack and also her debut album Tougher Than Love. It reached #13 on the Billboard Hot 100 in the U.S.. It peaked at number 2 in the UK.


     Two versions of the music video were made : one was in black and white for the "Tougher Than Love" album ; the other was made for the Bad Boys soundtrack, and Will Smith and Martin Laurence appeared in it.


                                ***Shy Guy.***

                                      Enjoy!
